description: Juice Wave’s mission is to refresh and nourish the soul with fresh pressed juices and smoothies by using the best quality ingredients fresh from local farms reflecting the growing seasons in Southern California, and to helping save the environment by practicing sustainability.To learn about Chef Arleigh Rose's journey from chef and farmer to food truck owner, and how she sources her ingredients, checking the quality every single time, read the Roaming Hunger blog here: http://roaminghunger.com/blog/6526/juice-wave-truck-san-diego-good-ingredients-for-a-happy-soul
name: Juice Wave
